<h2>Overview</h2>
<p>
    IEEE VR provides a unique opportunity for your organization to reach the world's foremost virtual reality researchers and application builders. We invite companies, government organizations, and academic institutions to showcase virtual reality related products â€“ hardware, software, integrated systems, peripherals, innovations, or literature in one of our two dedicated exhibit areas.
</p>
<p>
    Look forward to meeting with VR professionals eager to see what your company has to offer. Refreshments and a special reception will take place in the exhibit areas, ensuring good foot traffic to your display.
</p>

